//dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox won every round before taking out the four-paddler final on Monday at the Vaires-sur-Marne Nautical Stadium.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9998411110977318, \"rank\": 0.00012190328110548819, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 937, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1804605731497918e-19, \"text\": \"Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vaires-sur-Marne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox crossed the line ahead of France's Angele Hug with Great Britain's reigning world champion Kimberley Woods winning bronze.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1083, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 957, \"end\": 960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9998411110977318, \"rank\": 0.00012190328110548819, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6562985017535278, \"rank\": 0.523152354307892, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_a