noe_Slalom_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Canoe_Slalom_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.982435048408434e-22, \"text\": \"K1\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K-1\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympics titles\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrestling_at_the_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their mother Myriam Fox-Jerusalmi is also an Olympic medallist, winning a K1 bronze for France at the 1996 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1466, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.687856117580403e-16, \"text\": \"Myriam\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Myriam_Montemayor_Cruz\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6562985017535278, \"rank\": 0.523152354307892, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's crazy that it's mine,\\\" Noemie said of the gold medal.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not really dare to dream this big, but I really did this time and I dared to dream to get to the Olympics and then to get to that final.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I saw in the last up (gate) that I was first, it was pure joy - there is no words to describe that feeling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox was joined in the water by 30-year-old Jessica, who jumped in to celebrate after cheering her sibling along the course.\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.9998411110977318, \"rank\": 0.00012190328110548819, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While Noemie has long been a world-class paddler, she's never been able to compete in an Olympics before with her superstar sister taking the only Australian selection spot available.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9649071570307902, \"rank\": 0.036368567432682596, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The younger sibling said there were many times she considered giving the sport away, such was her sister's dominance.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jack Robinson has claimed silver in Olympic surfing, falling to local Kauli Vaast in the gold-medal match in Tahiti.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9985623829288852, \"rank\": 0.0014392684340246828, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"score\": 0.997915700882507, \"rank\": 0.001918538862553806, \"text\": \"Robinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Robinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2329, \"end\": 2335, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999798201318, \"rank\": 2.0178358800456315e-08, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Margaret River-raised surfer beat three-time world champion Gabriel Medina of Brazil earlier on Tuesday (AEST) to claim a place in the showpiece final.\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Medina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 2420, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999967929567486, \"rank\": 2.8076916254321323e-06, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2447, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he fell 17.67 to 7.83 in the decider to the popular Vaast, who grew up kilometres from Teahupo'o, first riding the infamous break at age eight.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2551, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vaast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vedast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By beating Medina and winning silver, he produced Australia's best result in Olympic surfing, after Owen Wright won bronze at the discipline's first Games in Tokyo 2021.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2655, \"end\": 2661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.281531028369967e-32, \"text\": \"Medina\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Medina\"}, {\"begin\": 2694, \"end\": 2703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9633614784831475, \"rank\": 0.03793670582045666, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 2744, \"end\": 2755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Owen_Wright_(rugby_league)\", \"score\": 0.5312492646259531, \"rank\": 0.647058823529425, \"text\": \"Owen Wright\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Owen_Wright_(rugby_league)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Owen_Wright_(rugby_league)\"}, {\"begin\": 2802, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999999959445631, \"rank\": 4.05510311664442e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Half a lifetime since becoming an Olympic teenage sensation, Melissa Wu has plunged into the record books again by diving for Australia in a record fifth Games - and reaching a fifth 10-metre platform final.\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 3022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2876, \"end\": 2886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Wu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Melissa Wu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Wu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melissa_Wu\"}, {\"begin\": 2941, \"end\": 2950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9633614784831475, \"rank\": 0.03793670582045666, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet while the 32-year-old celebrated her landmark performance in Paris, she was just as excited about the performance of Ellie Cole, a Sydney schoolgirl who has always idolised her.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3089, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.8738281939584014e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3159, \"end\": 3165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.461494827564607e-13, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The elegant 17-year-old eclipsed her hero, finishing as the sixth-best qualifier from the semi-finals with her five dives scoring 309.90 points, while Wu edged in as the 11th of the dozen finalists on 294.10.\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3358, \"end\": 3360, \"title\": \"htt